Mislav Mironovic was one of the first MTB freeride athletes in Croatia who became a professional and got the attention of well known international companies like Red Bull, Norco bikes, GoPro, Nokia, etc. Maybe he wasn’t the craziest when it comes to tricks but he was crazy enough to think he can succeed in everything he put's his mind into and so he did. From becoming a fully professional MTB athlete to a content creator that creates captivating smART/content through photography, short videos, and recently stop animation.

@loodclips 

We talked about how society influenced his mindset, his first obsession MTB freeride, how Red Bull helped him achieve his dreams, and much more.

